options.content:
## SIP Response Code Guide

### ‚úÖ Normal User Actions (Not Errors)
| Code | Meaning | Action Required |
|------|---------|----------------|
| **486** | Busy Here | ‚úÖ User is on another call - **NORMAL** |
| **603** | Decline | ‚úÖ User declined the call - **NORMAL** |
| **487** | Request Terminated | ‚úÖ Caller cancelled - **NORMAL** |
| **600** | Busy Everywhere | ‚úÖ All user devices busy - **NORMAL** |

### ‚ö†Ô∏è Client/Configuration Issues
| Code | Meaning | Action Required |
|------|---------|----------------|
| **401** | Unauthorized | üîç Check SIP credentials/authentication |
| **403** | Forbidden | üîç Check permissions/routing rules |
| **404** | Not Found | üîç Check dial plan/user exists |
| **407** | Proxy Auth Required | üîç Check proxy authentication |
| **480** | Temporarily Unavailable | üîç User not registered/unreachable |
| **484** | Address Incomplete | üîç Invalid phone number format |

### üö® Server Errors (YOUR SYSTEM)
| Code | Meaning | Action Required |
|------|---------|----------------|
| **500** | Internal Server Error | üö® **CRITICAL** - Check logs immediately |
| **503** | Service Unavailable | üö® **CRITICAL** - System overload/down |
| **504** | Server Timeout | üö® Check downstream service response times |

---

## Quick Diagnosis

**High 486/603**: ‚úÖ Normal - Users busy/declining  
**High 404/480**: ‚ö†Ô∏è Routing/registration issues  
**High 401/403**: ‚ö†Ô∏è Authentication problems  
**Any 5xx**: üö® **System problem - investigate immediately**
